body: Thanks @ebrevdo for the review. The previous build failure in `//tensorflow/core:api_test` was caused by the docstring changes. I have applied `tensorflow/core/api_def/update_api_def.sh` to fix it. This is just to accommodate the changes in doc string of the API, there is no actual API changes.
